creator: Fire Bionic
descriptionHtml:
A tracking app based on scientific research that will help you achieve your vision!

What distinguishes you from a pro-athlete / musician / scientist / artist / craftsperson? Simply said: the amount of practice and work they dedicated into their skill. If you’ve been dreaming of the same skillset, then let’s get started with this app.

Growth tracker encourages you to define the skills you want to improve as seeds. And if you take care of your skill seed by practicing, it will grow and blossom someday.

Define your schedules by adding in seeds and specifying how often you want to practice it. Growth tracker will remind you of your scheduled practicing times and will motivate to stick to your vision.

You can see your own growth progress in the statistics section. Growth tracker focuses on consistency over perfection. Your practice may have turned out shorter than scheduled? Never mind, progress is not a linear path to success. It is a bumpy road. So, every time slot you dedicate for your skillset is important time you have invested. Growth tracker will also keep you motivated with notifications that remind you to stick to growth mindset.

Start today by downloading the growth tracker app! And soon with it you will master the skill you have dreamed of!
descriptionShort: A tracker that truly empowers you on your own journey to personal growth.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Brand new revision of the novel tracker. Handle your seeds and schedules independently. Now with a Badge collection to show you what you accomplished!
